long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension removes the prefix from downloads.

For example, y2mate prefixes their downloads with "y2mate.com -". This extension removes this. Currently this is the only added extension. You can contribute on GitHub.
- https://github.com/emiel04/PrefixRemover
